## Limitations

This report is based on available literature and discussions up to October 2023. The findings are subject to the limitations of the sources used, which may not cover all geographic regions or account for all potential impacts of free public transport. Additionally, the long-term financial implications and sustainability of fare-free systems require further empirical study and analysis.